WEBVTT

00:56.973 --> 00:59.017
I had a basketball game today.

01:00.310 --> 01:02.270
Were you with Gi-seok?

01:05.356 --> 01:06.357
I was.

01:08.068 --> 01:09.319
Are you still with him?

01:11.362 --> 01:12.363
Yes.

01:13.323 --> 01:14.365
Then I'll hang up.

01:16.034 --> 01:17.035
Why?

01:18.870 --> 01:19.871
Ji-ho...

01:21.414 --> 01:22.457
Don't hang up.

01:24.667 --> 01:25.710
What's gotten into you?

01:26.920 --> 01:28.546
It's nothing urgent.

01:29.547 --> 01:30.590
We can talk later.

01:30.673 --> 01:32.842
Gi-seok, can you drop me off somewhere?

01:33.885 --> 01:36.429
Are you getting off instead of joining us?

01:53.613 --> 01:54.614
What's wrong?

01:58.660 --> 02:00.370
What? Did you get into an argument?

02:12.465 --> 02:13.508
Jeez.

02:16.010 --> 02:17.887
Now I feel like I should apologize.

02:19.597 --> 02:21.057
For pushing you to pick up.

04:27.225 --> 04:29.060
What's wrong with him?

04:30.561 --> 04:32.146
Did Ji-ho say where he was going?

04:32.647 --> 04:34.232
Stop calling him and let him be.

04:35.024 --> 04:37.110
- Where did he go?
- To see a girl.

04:37.944 --> 04:39.696
- What?
- Really?

04:40.280 --> 04:41.406
You said he had someone.

04:42.031 --> 04:44.867
Not really.
He said he was trying to end things.

04:45.618 --> 04:47.912
On the contrary.
He's burning with passion for her.

04:50.123 --> 04:51.165
Really?

04:52.292 --> 04:53.960
I can't wait to find out about her.

05:26.993 --> 05:28.328
You're going to yell, right?

05:30.955 --> 05:32.415
Let's go somewhere less crowded.

06:01.069 --> 06:02.070
Go ahead.

06:07.492 --> 06:08.576
Should I go first?

06:16.000 --> 06:17.043
"I'm sorry.

06:17.919 --> 06:19.170
I was caught off guard.

06:20.630 --> 06:23.216
How could we keep on talking
with Gi-seok next to you?"

06:25.176 --> 06:26.761
You did it to protect me, right?

06:29.055 --> 06:30.807
Why not just put him on the phone?

06:31.891 --> 06:33.142
If you wanted to be bold,

06:33.726 --> 06:35.686
you should've told him it was me.

06:37.730 --> 06:38.773
I can't.

06:44.028 --> 06:47.365
I'm a loser
who's too scared to take any risks.

06:50.326 --> 06:51.452
I asked for your help.

06:53.329 --> 06:55.331
I asked you to help me move on.

06:55.748 --> 06:57.125
Why must I do that?

06:58.042 --> 07:00.586
Who am I to care
if you're developing feelings for me?

07:01.295 --> 07:04.298
I can barely contain
my own heart from exploding.

07:05.091 --> 07:08.219
Why should I care
if your heart gets crushed or not?

07:11.431 --> 07:12.515
I come first.

07:14.392 --> 07:15.768
What I want is my priority.

07:16.978 --> 07:19.313
I don't care
if you go insane in the process.

07:26.863 --> 07:27.947
Wait, are you leaving?

07:28.030 --> 07:30.408
My girlfriend's pissed.
Gi-seok, see you around.

07:30.491 --> 07:31.951
- Bye, guys.
- Seriously?

07:32.410 --> 07:34.537
- Whatever.
- Fine, get going, then.

07:34.620 --> 07:37.165
His girlfriend has a short leash on him.

07:37.248 --> 07:38.749
I'm jealous, though.

07:40.001 --> 07:41.627
I'd love to be kept on a leash too.

07:42.545 --> 07:43.963
Then get yourself a girlfriend.

07:45.798 --> 07:48.092
Are you really in a position
to hand out advice?

07:51.179 --> 07:52.180
What do you mean?

07:53.014 --> 07:55.933
You're constantly arguing
with your girlfriend these days.

08:13.784 --> 08:16.245
Hey, follow me out, will you?

08:18.623 --> 08:20.583
- What's wrong?
- I just want to talk.

08:20.666 --> 08:22.418
- Why?
- What's wrong?

08:22.710 --> 08:24.962
- What happened?
- What's going on?

08:27.798 --> 08:29.592
I was going to let it slide...

08:31.135 --> 08:34.597
since I'm older
and my girlfriend was mixed up in it,

08:35.556 --> 08:37.558
but how could your friends be so clueless?

08:39.852 --> 08:41.896
Don't they know what's appropriate or not?

08:41.979 --> 08:43.981
How can they walk in
to my girlfriend's home?

08:44.732 --> 08:46.692
- Her sister--
- Ji-ho's worse.

08:47.318 --> 08:49.487
He's seeing someone,

08:49.946 --> 08:52.156
so even though he was forced there,

08:53.366 --> 08:55.910
he shouldn't have
drunk all night at their place.

08:57.161 --> 08:58.329
Is he that thoughtless?

08:58.412 --> 09:00.498
He's not normally like that.

09:01.541 --> 09:03.668
- No?
- No, he's not.

09:03.751 --> 09:05.294
Then we have a bigger problem.

09:08.297 --> 09:09.632
Remember how he...

09:12.426 --> 09:14.512
got wound up on the day we had drinks?

09:16.514 --> 09:18.015
You're saying it meant something.

09:18.099 --> 09:20.518
- Ji-ho was drunk that night--
- Does he...

09:22.395 --> 09:23.688
like my girlfriend?

09:24.480 --> 09:25.606
What?

09:27.400 --> 09:28.859
Unbelievable.

09:30.736 --> 09:32.863
How can you even say such a thing?

09:32.947 --> 09:34.991
- Is that so?
- Yes.

09:35.992 --> 09:38.119
You don't know about
the woman he's seeing,

09:38.953 --> 09:40.413
so how can you be sure?

09:40.496 --> 09:42.331
The same goes for you.

09:43.124 --> 09:45.793
Did your girlfriend say
that Ji-ho likes her?

09:47.837 --> 09:49.839
You know what? You're pissing me off.

09:51.048 --> 09:53.384
I agree that my friends were idiots,

09:53.467 --> 09:56.470
but you make them sound like dirty pigs
who hit on random women.

09:57.722 --> 09:58.931
It's disturbing to hear.

10:12.069 --> 10:13.821
Let's forget about it, then.

10:14.989 --> 10:15.990
Jeez.

10:19.493 --> 10:20.745
Damn it.

10:34.925 --> 10:37.261
- Have you been drinking?
- How could I not?

10:37.887 --> 10:41.766
I've been getting so much shit
because of your stupidity.

10:42.266 --> 10:44.185
Is it about that night at Jae-in's house?

10:44.268 --> 10:45.561
I already explained that.

10:45.645 --> 10:46.896
Whatever.

10:46.979 --> 10:50.107
Don't ever go near
Gi-seok's girlfriend or her sister again.

10:50.941 --> 10:53.486
What's going on? Did something happen?

10:54.195 --> 10:55.821
Just do as I say!

10:56.489 --> 10:57.782
Tell Ji-ho too.

10:58.407 --> 11:00.451
Also, shouldn't you be busy studying?

11:00.910 --> 11:02.328
No wonder you never pass.

11:13.714 --> 11:15.049
YEONG-JAE

11:15.132 --> 11:16.384
Did something happen?

11:16.759 --> 11:18.010
Hyeon-su's pissed.

11:32.441 --> 11:34.068
Do you just need me to stay hidden?

11:39.323 --> 11:41.826
I know your situation
and what you're going through.

11:43.703 --> 11:46.205
I understand,
but I still get angry from time to time.

11:47.373 --> 11:48.708
That's what happened today.

11:51.961 --> 11:54.088
Even when I was getting mad at you,

11:55.881 --> 11:57.341
I realized it was wrong.

12:09.145 --> 12:10.312
I like you a lot.

12:15.568 --> 12:17.445
I'm not in a position to fight for you,

12:18.070 --> 12:19.655
but I'm too scared to cut you off.

12:20.281 --> 12:21.407
I feel like...

12:22.742 --> 12:23.993
I'm doomed...

12:25.703 --> 12:28.581
because my love for you
grows bigger by the day.

12:31.542 --> 12:33.627
When you told Gi-seok it was over,

12:33.711 --> 12:36.672
although I said
that it wasn't what I wanted,

12:36.756 --> 12:38.090
secretly...

12:41.218 --> 12:43.387
I thought about not being good enough
for you.

12:44.680 --> 12:47.933
I started worrying about
how you'd soon figure that out.

12:49.268 --> 12:50.436
What a loser, right?

12:55.691 --> 12:57.443
Even though I say you had nothing...

12:59.195 --> 13:01.363
to do with my decision
to break up with Gi-seok,

13:02.948 --> 13:04.408
no one will believe it.

13:07.286 --> 13:08.996
They'll point fingers at you too.

13:09.580 --> 13:11.415
I don't care about any of that.

13:15.753 --> 13:17.463
To be honest, I'm still not sure.

13:19.006 --> 13:20.549
I don't know what I want.

13:22.051 --> 13:24.720
In terms of a boyfriend or a husband.

13:27.515 --> 13:28.724
All I know right now

13:29.892 --> 13:32.520
is that I'm not happy
with my current situation.

13:33.687 --> 13:37.608
I know very well that no relationship
burns passionately every day.

13:40.027 --> 13:42.863
And it's impossible
for couples to never hurt each other.

13:45.366 --> 13:49.119
You can call me immature if you want,
but I still long for those things.

13:52.623 --> 13:54.959
A relationship
where I'm not the only passionate one

13:57.795 --> 13:58.838
and the kind of love

14:00.256 --> 14:02.091
where I don't get hurt.

14:06.804 --> 14:10.266
To be honest, I haven't even thought about

14:11.433 --> 14:12.768
starting something with you.

14:17.022 --> 14:19.567
- I mean--
- I'm not upset.

14:22.236 --> 14:23.654
I understand it all too well.

14:26.448 --> 14:27.616
You must feel stuck.

14:29.952 --> 14:32.872
Overcoming the difficulties
and obstacles together?

14:35.082 --> 14:36.125
That's a myth.

14:37.418 --> 14:40.045
Once you become
more objective on the matter,

14:42.506 --> 14:44.884
then I'll accept it all
without resentment.

14:45.384 --> 14:46.552
What a liar.

14:48.345 --> 14:49.722
If I tell you that it's over

14:50.389 --> 14:52.558
and that we should go back
to being strangers,

14:53.601 --> 14:54.810
you'll just accept that?

14:59.607 --> 15:00.733
Right now I will.

15:05.112 --> 15:07.239
After time passes,

15:11.243 --> 15:13.287
if you still feel the same way,

15:17.082 --> 15:18.208
come to me then.

15:28.344 --> 15:29.553
Even if it's when...

15:30.846 --> 15:32.473
I'm old and wrinkly?

15:36.310 --> 15:37.311
Yes.

17:12.948 --> 17:13.991
Hello?

17:15.034 --> 17:16.326
Don't turn around.

17:20.664 --> 17:21.790
If you do,

17:23.459 --> 17:25.669
I won't let you leave me.

17:30.424 --> 17:31.425
After many years,

17:32.426 --> 17:35.054
if I come to you then,

17:38.348 --> 17:39.933
will you really accept me?

17:42.102 --> 17:44.104
You'll probably cling on until I do.

17:47.524 --> 17:49.777
Don't fall in love
with anyone else until then.

18:03.123 --> 18:04.333
I'm a mean person.

18:05.375 --> 18:06.543
I'm selfish too.

18:08.837 --> 18:10.172
Resent me all you want.

18:10.672 --> 18:12.174
I can handle your resentment.

18:15.677 --> 18:17.638
Just don't fall in love with anyone else.

18:21.683 --> 18:22.976
You're unbelievable.

18:23.602 --> 18:24.728
I said I'm mean.

18:28.023 --> 18:29.024
When I...

18:31.193 --> 18:32.653
finally make my way to you,

18:35.447 --> 18:37.032
I promise to protect you

18:38.075 --> 18:40.369
from all the criticism and judgment.

18:48.502 --> 18:49.545
That's what...

18:50.420 --> 18:51.880
I wanted to tell you today.

18:56.009 --> 18:57.803
I won't hurt you anymore.

19:04.184 --> 19:05.602
So promise you'll wait for me.

19:25.497 --> 19:27.040
You can take as long as you want.

19:28.083 --> 19:29.543
Just as long as you come to me.

19:32.171 --> 19:33.964
I'll wait no matter how long it takes.

20:31.438 --> 20:36.985
PHARMACIST

21:42.259 --> 21:43.969
This is nice.

21:45.053 --> 21:46.096
Unbelievable.

21:50.142 --> 21:52.185
Thank you. Please enjoy.

21:55.605 --> 21:58.275
Being jobless is the life, isn't it?

21:58.775 --> 22:01.278
You wake up at noon and mooch off others.

22:02.154 --> 22:05.449
Don't you feel guilty to watch your sister
go to work every morning?

22:06.366 --> 22:08.618
I do all the dishes and laundry for her.

22:09.286 --> 22:11.330
You should, since you're putting her out.

22:13.040 --> 22:14.124
I'm just saying.

22:19.046 --> 22:20.380
How's Jeong-in these days?

22:24.259 --> 22:25.927
I told you to keep an eye on her.

22:27.721 --> 22:28.930
I have been.

22:33.101 --> 22:36.229
How is her relationship with Gi-seok?

22:37.147 --> 22:39.149
He came over for wine a few days ago.

22:39.232 --> 22:40.484
Really?

22:41.693 --> 22:43.362
How do you think they're doing?

22:43.445 --> 22:46.198
- Well, you know...
- Just tell me as it is.

22:53.830 --> 22:55.374
She looked sad.

23:03.965 --> 23:05.467
ARCHIVE
RESTRICTED AREA

23:22.192 --> 23:26.613
UNEXPECTEDLY YOU

23:30.742 --> 23:32.202
Are you gloating?

23:34.913 --> 23:37.541
It is an ambitious project
full of your ulterior motive.

23:38.708 --> 23:41.211
- Jealous much?
- As if.

23:41.753 --> 23:44.172
I hate relationships
that only give you headaches.

23:47.300 --> 23:48.593
He said he'll wait for me.

23:50.095 --> 23:52.055
Now that's not something
you hear every day.

23:54.307 --> 23:56.852
- Jealous much?
- In this case, yes.

23:57.477 --> 23:59.354
Did he say he'll wait unconditionally?

24:01.314 --> 24:02.399
Yes.

24:17.956 --> 24:20.625
You should just say it.
I'll have indigestion at this rate.

24:27.841 --> 24:28.925
What if...

24:30.719 --> 24:34.556
you were about to do something that might
make everyone turn their backs on you?

24:36.391 --> 24:37.559
What would you do?

24:39.478 --> 24:40.604
Move forward

24:41.438 --> 24:42.355
or give up?

24:45.734 --> 24:48.653
The choice will vary
depending on what exactly it is.

24:49.779 --> 24:52.491
However, something that is
frowned upon by everyone

24:52.574 --> 24:54.367
can't be right.

24:55.035 --> 24:56.870
It means that it's a reckless decision.

24:59.915 --> 25:01.208
Is it the pharmacist?

25:03.001 --> 25:04.085
No.

25:05.003 --> 25:06.171
Why not?

25:06.796 --> 25:08.048
Is there an issue with him?

25:10.800 --> 25:11.760
Of course not.

25:18.350 --> 25:19.267
Does he...

25:20.477 --> 25:21.686
have a girlfriend?

25:25.148 --> 25:27.025
Then what could be the issue?

25:28.360 --> 25:29.945
I'm the one with the issue.

25:36.868 --> 25:39.037
What are you going to do
about your boyfriend?

25:40.997 --> 25:42.666
We're going to meet tonight.

25:44.417 --> 25:45.585
Are you going to end it?

25:46.795 --> 25:47.629
Yes.

25:50.006 --> 25:51.299
You must feel awful.

25:53.301 --> 25:54.970
I was going to do it anyway.

25:56.972 --> 25:59.516
Why do relationships
always have shitty endings?

26:04.437 --> 26:05.480
Hey, join us.

26:27.168 --> 26:29.129
- Ji-ho.
- Hey, you just got here.

26:29.713 --> 26:30.922
Eat a few bites first.

26:31.715 --> 26:34.092
- Let's eat.
- How dense are you two?

26:35.468 --> 26:37.679
Ji-ho, you know what I'll say, right?

26:42.350 --> 26:43.768
Your suspicions are correct.

26:47.814 --> 26:48.857
Why?

26:49.149 --> 26:50.108
"Why?"

26:50.817 --> 26:51.735
Hey.

26:52.193 --> 26:54.988
Out of all the women,
why did it have to be Gi-seok's girl?

26:56.156 --> 26:57.282
You think I'll lose?

26:57.949 --> 27:01.703
Shut up for a second.
Have you been seeing her all this time?

27:06.708 --> 27:07.751
We knew each other...

27:10.295 --> 27:12.130
before Gi-seok introduced her to us.

27:13.757 --> 27:15.425
I asked her out,

27:16.134 --> 27:18.595
but she said she was taken,
so we remained friends.

27:19.137 --> 27:21.890
Men and women can't be friends. Right?

27:22.599 --> 27:24.768
Well, it's not impossible.

27:24.851 --> 27:27.395
So? Are the two of you still just friends?

27:31.608 --> 27:34.319
No, I like her more than just a friend.

27:34.736 --> 27:36.029
What are you saying?

27:37.614 --> 27:40.325
Anyway, okay. That's how you feel.
Then what about her?

27:42.869 --> 27:44.287
She feels the same way.

27:52.962 --> 27:55.006
Would a one-sided crush have been better?

27:56.132 --> 27:58.593
No, not really. Right?

27:59.636 --> 28:00.845
Yes. That is true,

28:02.889 --> 28:03.973
but she's...

28:05.225 --> 28:07.477
She's so weird.

28:08.186 --> 28:10.605
Then what is she going to do
with her boyfriend?

28:10.689 --> 28:12.315
She's taken. How can she do that?

28:14.067 --> 28:15.443
Hey, I have a kid.

28:33.628 --> 28:34.754
So what will you do now?

28:35.422 --> 28:37.006
Will you steal her from Gi-seok?

28:38.967 --> 28:40.427
Well, I'm just saying.

28:41.177 --> 28:43.972
Ji-ho said Jeong-in likes him
more than just a friend as well.

28:44.055 --> 28:45.807
Then she should break up with Gi-seok.

28:46.641 --> 28:47.892
It doesn't matter to me.

28:49.269 --> 28:50.520
What's this nonsense now?

28:52.814 --> 28:55.024
I knew about her boyfriend
from the get-go,

28:55.108 --> 28:56.776
so I should've given up back then.

28:57.318 --> 29:00.321
As you guys know, it's not easy
for a woman to accept my situation.

29:00.405 --> 29:02.532
It'd be selfish of me
to ask her to choose me.

29:04.701 --> 29:07.537
Still, don't you think
she needs to make up her mind?

29:07.620 --> 29:08.955
That's what I'm saying.

29:09.831 --> 29:12.417
The fact that I'm in her life
is a lot for her to handle.

29:13.168 --> 29:14.669
I don't want to make it harder.

29:41.780 --> 29:42.822
Where are you?

29:42.906 --> 29:46.409
Hey, I'm so sorry. It doesn't look like
the director will leave anytime soon.

29:48.745 --> 29:50.288
You said you'd just have dinner.

29:51.039 --> 29:52.165
That was the plan,

29:53.666 --> 29:56.669
but other teams joined us,
so it's turned into a big thing now.

30:01.925 --> 30:03.760
Let's just meet tomorrow instead, okay?

30:04.302 --> 30:05.845
I'll treat you to a nice dinner.

30:07.388 --> 30:08.765
You have a job,

30:09.307 --> 30:12.143
so I don't want you to think of me
as your number-one priority.

30:13.394 --> 30:15.021
But whenever anything happens,

30:15.438 --> 30:18.483
you cancel or bail on me first.
How am I supposed to interpret it?

30:19.275 --> 30:20.443
Because it's no big deal?

30:21.986 --> 30:26.074
No, it's not that. I guess I do it because
you've always been so understanding.

30:30.328 --> 30:31.871
So it's my fault?

30:32.580 --> 30:34.165
Don't twist my words around, okay?

30:35.083 --> 30:36.209
All right, I heard you.

30:37.752 --> 30:39.963
This won't happen again. Are we good now?

30:41.339 --> 30:43.091
Is this the "love" you talked about?

30:43.675 --> 30:45.301
All right, I'll leave now.

30:47.929 --> 30:50.348
I'm tired of going through this
over and over again.

30:50.932 --> 30:54.102
You always do things reluctantly
and make such a big deal out of them.

30:55.228 --> 30:57.230
Why do I always have to beg you?

30:59.983 --> 31:02.443
Go home and wait for me.
I'll be there shortly, okay?

31:03.820 --> 31:05.196
It won't change anything.

31:05.989 --> 31:08.074
- I wanted to say--
- I've made it clear to you.

31:09.701 --> 31:11.286
We can't break up.

31:12.620 --> 31:15.957
That uncertainty is really the only thing
that kept us together until now.

31:22.005 --> 31:23.464
I know we should talk in person.

31:24.299 --> 31:26.968
Let's meet up sometime soon.
We'll end things in person.

31:29.137 --> 31:31.389
I said we should start over, didn't I?

31:32.849 --> 31:34.100
I told you I'll try harder.

31:34.183 --> 31:37.353
Then you should at least give me some time
and see what happens.

31:37.437 --> 31:39.314
If you keep saying you want to break up,

31:39.397 --> 31:41.024
- what can--
- Hey, are you fighting?

31:42.150 --> 31:43.484
Hey, who are you talking to?

31:44.861 --> 31:46.029
Get back inside.

32:27.779 --> 32:28.738
Hey.

32:28.821 --> 32:30.740
Where are you? Are you at home?

32:31.532 --> 32:32.575
No, I'm at the office.

32:33.368 --> 32:36.371
The book club meeting is tomorrow,
so I wanted to get things ready.

32:38.289 --> 32:40.750
What's up?
Did you and Gi-seok already part ways?

32:42.043 --> 32:44.545
I couldn't see him today.
He's out for a team dinner.

32:45.380 --> 32:46.923
Jeez, he's the worst.

32:47.382 --> 32:48.758
Is he avoiding you on purpose?

32:49.968 --> 32:50.969
I don't know.

32:51.427 --> 32:53.763
I'll head out shortly.
Where are you going to be?

33:11.739 --> 33:14.033
- Has she been coming over?
- No, it's not that.

33:17.912 --> 33:19.330
- Hey, let's go.
- What?

33:20.081 --> 33:22.583
- Come on. We should get going.
- I have to talk to Ji-ho.

33:22.667 --> 33:24.627
No, you don't. Shut up. Bye.

33:34.554 --> 33:36.347
I don't think your friend is home yet.

33:37.432 --> 33:38.558
She'll be home shortly.

33:45.940 --> 33:47.275
You don't know her door code?

33:47.358 --> 33:49.235
- Have you had dinner yet?
- Yes.

33:50.194 --> 33:52.113
- All right, then.
- Let's go grab some food.

33:53.281 --> 33:54.365
You said you've eaten.

33:55.366 --> 33:56.534
I'll watch you eat.

33:57.577 --> 33:59.037
But you won't buy me dinner?

34:01.330 --> 34:02.498
I don't have my wallet.

34:03.207 --> 34:04.667
Even if you did, you wouldn't.

34:10.798 --> 34:12.258
Here are your noodles.

34:15.470 --> 34:16.429
Here you go.

34:16.929 --> 34:18.389
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

34:19.015 --> 34:21.059
- You can add this seasoning.
- Okay, thank you.

34:21.142 --> 34:22.226
- Thank you.
- Enjoy.

34:28.649 --> 34:29.525
It looks so good.

34:32.070 --> 34:33.279
Can you really eat both?

34:35.740 --> 34:36.908
You're not getting any.

34:47.543 --> 34:48.753
I said I'd watch you eat.

34:50.213 --> 34:51.881
I feel like a monkey in the zoo.

35:01.349 --> 35:02.725
By the way, your friends...

35:03.601 --> 35:05.144
It's okay. I told them briefly.

35:06.145 --> 35:06.979
What did they say?

35:08.439 --> 35:11.526
They're probably more surprised with me.

35:15.238 --> 35:18.407
Were you really
going to stay single forever?

35:20.159 --> 35:21.369
I wouldn't say that,

35:21.452 --> 35:23.704
but I never thought about it
or made any effort.

35:28.000 --> 35:29.085
What are you thinking?

35:29.961 --> 35:31.838
What? Nothing.

35:34.882 --> 35:37.218
About my story...
I'll tell you everything later on.

35:41.889 --> 35:43.558
You really aren't even offering.

35:47.436 --> 35:50.148
Fine, I'll be generous.
Just one bite, then.

36:21.554 --> 36:23.222
Stop bringing side dishes.

36:23.764 --> 36:25.975
We rarely eat at home,
so we never finish them.

36:29.520 --> 36:31.772
You and Si-hoon are having problems,
aren't you?

36:37.820 --> 36:39.447
Shall I ask Si-hoon directly?

36:43.993 --> 36:45.494
We're going to get a divorce.

36:49.582 --> 36:51.292
We don't live together at the moment.

36:52.293 --> 36:54.879
He refuses to sign
the divorce papers, so--

36:54.962 --> 36:56.255
Why do you want a divorce?

36:59.425 --> 37:00.468
Never mind.

37:01.844 --> 37:04.305
I have big respect for you
for holding out this long.

37:07.975 --> 37:08.976
I'm sorry.

37:11.771 --> 37:12.855
Well...

37:13.940 --> 37:15.316
What about your job?

37:16.108 --> 37:18.319
Will you have to quit if people find out?

37:18.736 --> 37:21.447
No, not really.
But I submitted my letter of resignation.

37:21.530 --> 37:23.658
It hasn't been processed yet, though.

37:23.741 --> 37:27.119
It's not like you're failing at your job.
Why would you quit?

37:28.829 --> 37:31.540
I want to go back to school.

37:32.750 --> 37:37.338
And I'm thinking of letting Jae-in
stay here for the time being.

37:39.048 --> 37:40.174
Jae-in? Why?

37:55.731 --> 37:57.525
Mom. Stay here.

38:08.202 --> 38:10.663
- Si-hoon, my--
- So you are here.

38:10.746 --> 38:12.373
Why didn't you pick up...

38:14.166 --> 38:15.668
- You should've called me--
- Mom.

38:15.751 --> 38:18.296
- Go in the room.
- Okay, I'll...

38:23.968 --> 38:25.678
I heard you two don't live together.

38:26.554 --> 38:29.181
That is also a promise,
but what the heck is this about?

38:30.766 --> 38:32.852
I have to talk to Seo-in about something.

38:32.935 --> 38:34.603
Then you should be more courteous.

38:35.062 --> 38:38.482
You kept ringing the doorbell and calling
as if she deserved to be scolded.

38:38.983 --> 38:40.609
Are you that ill-mannered?

38:43.696 --> 38:44.989
I'm disappointed in you.

38:46.365 --> 38:49.285
Are you sure you want things to work out
between the two of you?

38:50.286 --> 38:53.539
If you're going to keep this up,
I don't want you two to stay together.

38:53.998 --> 38:56.709
I'll make sure you two get a divorce.

39:04.383 --> 39:05.551
Going down.

39:10.556 --> 39:11.891
Basement, second floor.

39:15.019 --> 39:16.103
The doors are closing.

40:23.838 --> 40:25.089
We can get through this.

40:26.549 --> 40:27.633
I love you.

41:00.416 --> 41:01.500
Thanks for this.

41:16.223 --> 41:17.391
I just realized

41:19.935 --> 41:22.313
that you always thank me,
even for things like this.

41:26.275 --> 41:27.401
This is so unlike you.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.653
Just be your usual self.

41:31.947 --> 41:33.157
I'm just anxious, I guess.

41:38.037 --> 41:40.289
I admit that I got too comfortable.

41:42.708 --> 41:43.918
I've told you many times,

41:46.795 --> 41:49.590
but I never imagined us breaking up.

41:51.800 --> 41:53.677
Yet you always talked about breaking up?

41:56.972 --> 41:59.517
You know how I am. I have a short fuse.

42:02.686 --> 42:04.480
It's no use talking about the past.

42:06.232 --> 42:07.650
- Let's--
- I can't agree to it.

42:09.443 --> 42:11.445
- Gi-seok.
- Let's try to make things work.

42:14.532 --> 42:16.408
I'll accept it if we can't work it out.

42:20.955 --> 42:22.331
My father wants to see you.

42:25.668 --> 42:26.710
It wasn't me.

42:29.171 --> 42:30.464
You can ask him directly.

42:31.465 --> 42:32.841
He told me to bring you over.

42:37.054 --> 42:39.265
I'll talk to him
if you're too uncomfortable.

42:39.348 --> 42:40.516
No, it's okay.

42:42.184 --> 42:43.352
I'll meet him.

42:49.066 --> 42:50.109
Gi-seok.

42:53.445 --> 42:55.990
You don't have to come
when I'm meeting your father.

42:57.366 --> 42:58.867
I'd rather meet with him alone.

43:01.662 --> 43:04.790
I'm only going to talk about myself.
That's why I'm asking you this.

43:05.708 --> 43:06.834
Let me meet him alone.

43:16.552 --> 43:18.887
All right. Go ahead and meet him
without me, then.

44:09.480 --> 44:12.232
It stimulates a bowel movement,
so take it before meals.

44:12.316 --> 44:14.276
- I've been taking it, so I'm aware.
- I see.

44:14.360 --> 44:16.153
- Have a nice day.
- Thank you. You too.

44:18.280 --> 44:19.865
- Have a nice day.
- Have a nice day.

44:19.948 --> 44:21.367
- Has it been busy?
- No.

44:22.201 --> 44:24.453
The new udon place at the intersection
is so good.

44:24.787 --> 44:25.829
I should check it out.

44:25.913 --> 44:28.123
You two should eat together
starting tomorrow.

44:28.207 --> 44:29.625
No, people will gossip.

44:32.127 --> 44:33.504
It's not good for Ye-seul.

44:34.171 --> 44:35.047
Why is that?

44:35.464 --> 44:38.217
Well... Other store owners gossip a lot,
you know.

44:39.635 --> 44:43.138
Will you not even talk to us
when you get into a relationship?

44:43.222 --> 44:44.348
Jeez, cut it out.

44:44.723 --> 44:46.308
Are you seeing someone?

44:46.684 --> 44:47.685
No, I'm not.

44:49.061 --> 44:50.646
- Hello.
- Oh, it's Eun-u!

44:50.729 --> 44:52.189
Eun-u is here.

44:52.272 --> 44:53.774
- Hello.
- Hello.

44:54.608 --> 44:56.360
Eun-u, it's so good to see you!

44:56.443 --> 44:57.444
Hello.

44:58.320 --> 44:59.780
You're a big boy now.

45:02.282 --> 45:03.283
Eun-u!

45:03.784 --> 45:06.704
Mom, just eat. He'll come back
if he wants more food.

45:09.581 --> 45:12.209
You sound as if you've raised ten kids.

45:13.752 --> 45:14.920
Mom, you were worse.

45:15.462 --> 45:17.881
When I was little,
I thought I was a foundling.

45:20.467 --> 45:22.136
I was so strict with you,

45:22.594 --> 45:24.722
but I can't be like that with Eun-u.

45:25.472 --> 45:28.684
Even today, we left the house
as soon as he said he wanted to see you.

45:30.144 --> 45:32.062
I know it's not easy for you and Dad.

45:33.147 --> 45:34.606
Don't say that.

45:35.232 --> 45:36.400
If we didn't have Eun-u,

45:37.901 --> 45:40.195
your dad and I would be
so bored and listless.

45:42.364 --> 45:45.367
It won't take me long.
Hang in there just a little longer.

45:46.994 --> 45:48.328
Stop saying that, please.

45:52.583 --> 45:54.460
About the "teacher" at the library...

45:55.544 --> 45:56.712
I heard it's a woman.

45:58.964 --> 46:00.466
She's just someone I know.

46:01.967 --> 46:02.968
I see.

46:04.344 --> 46:05.345
Well...

46:06.221 --> 46:09.558
There's someone I want to set you up with.

46:12.728 --> 46:15.481
I'm bringing it up
just in case you're interested.

46:15.814 --> 46:17.149
If not, don't worry about it.

46:24.072 --> 46:25.532
There's someone I like.

46:27.910 --> 46:29.995
I'm not saying I'll act on it right away.

46:32.915 --> 46:33.957
My gosh.

46:39.588 --> 46:40.547
What's wrong?

46:44.343 --> 46:46.178
I'm just so happy to hear that.

46:49.598 --> 46:50.641
Thank you.

46:59.149 --> 47:00.150
Here.

47:10.869 --> 47:12.913
Eun-u will wonder what's going on.

47:16.542 --> 47:18.919
He always talked
as if he'd stay single forever.

47:19.461 --> 47:20.796
How can I not cry?

47:21.922 --> 47:24.633
If he says he's getting married,
you'll bawl your eyes out.

47:28.053 --> 47:29.805
Do you think that can happen?

47:31.306 --> 47:34.476
I couldn't ask him anything
because I didn't want to jinx it.

47:35.811 --> 47:37.229
Do you think she has a kid too?

47:38.522 --> 47:41.400
Won't it be a little challenging
if her kid isn't that young?

47:41.483 --> 47:42.818
Who cares?

47:42.901 --> 47:45.112
As long as the two of them
want to be together.

47:45.487 --> 47:47.865
Grandma, I want ice cream.

47:47.948 --> 47:51.243
Oh, okay. Grandpa will buy you ice cream.
Let's go.

47:52.202 --> 47:53.537
Off we go.

47:55.372 --> 47:56.415
Be careful.

48:05.257 --> 48:06.425
I'll get going, sir.

48:07.050 --> 48:08.135
Okay, thank you.

48:17.978 --> 48:18.979
Hello?

48:19.688 --> 48:21.982
Hello, this is Lee Jeong-in.

48:23.066 --> 48:24.109
Lee Jeong-in?

48:25.485 --> 48:27.821
Oh, you're Tae-hak's daughter, right?

48:28.572 --> 48:29.615
Yes.

48:31.116 --> 48:32.200
How do you do?

48:33.160 --> 48:35.245
I heard you said you'd like to meet me.

48:36.580 --> 48:37.664
Yes, I did.

48:39.041 --> 48:41.418
Why isn't Gi-seok arranging it?

48:42.377 --> 48:43.837
I'd like to meet you alone.

48:44.755 --> 48:47.758
If you would allow it,
I'd like to meet you without Gi-seok.

48:49.134 --> 48:50.218
Sure, let's do that.

48:51.470 --> 48:55.265
Please let me know the time and location
that work best for you, and I'll be there.

48:59.603 --> 49:01.104
Then I'll let you know...

49:02.773 --> 49:03.899
in a few days.

49:04.858 --> 49:06.985
All right, then.
I'll wait to hear from you.

49:08.278 --> 49:09.279
Sounds good.

49:20.248 --> 49:22.334
CIVIL SERVICE EXAM PREP COURSES

49:33.053 --> 49:34.054
Hi.

49:38.600 --> 49:40.560
- Where's your bag?
- It's in the study room.

49:41.561 --> 49:42.896
What brings you by this late?

49:42.980 --> 49:45.315
I just parted ways with my friends.
Let's hang out.

49:45.691 --> 49:48.193
No, I'm just going to study.

49:50.070 --> 49:51.071
Really?

49:51.947 --> 49:53.615
Okay. Then we'll hang out next time.

49:53.699 --> 49:55.534
Even next time, I'll have to study.

49:58.453 --> 50:01.790
I haven't been studying much,
so I'm starting to get a little anxious.

50:02.958 --> 50:04.835
And I'm being a nuisance, aren't I?

50:05.752 --> 50:07.754
Why are you taking it like that?

50:07.963 --> 50:09.214
That's what it sounds like.

50:09.297 --> 50:10.465
All right, then.

50:11.466 --> 50:12.884
I'll stop coming by.

50:15.429 --> 50:17.556
But I'll kill you
if you don't pass the exam.

50:33.196 --> 50:34.614
Put some lotion on your face.

50:35.949 --> 50:37.617
Yeong-jae rejected me.

50:39.578 --> 50:40.912
If he doesn't pass the exam,

50:40.996 --> 50:42.789
I'm going to pull all his hair out.

50:43.457 --> 50:44.791
He doesn't want to see you?

50:44.875 --> 50:46.793
No, he doesn't. He said he has to study.

50:49.963 --> 50:51.423
You should dump the pharmacist.

50:53.216 --> 50:54.551
I can't be the only reject.

51:01.391 --> 51:02.434
Jeong-in.

51:03.477 --> 51:04.770
Mom is worried about you.

51:07.647 --> 51:09.066
I'll assure her that I'm fine.

51:21.328 --> 51:24.664
That's okay. He probably wants to focus
on studying for the exam.

51:26.416 --> 51:28.585
I wonder if it's because of me.

51:28.835 --> 51:31.546
Yeong-jae isn't the type
to blame others and give excuses.

51:32.214 --> 51:33.298
Don't worry about it.

51:34.299 --> 51:36.426
I hope Jae-in's feelings aren't too hurt.

51:38.261 --> 51:41.264
Jae-in knows about you.

51:42.015 --> 51:44.017
I'm sorry. It just happened.

51:45.727 --> 51:46.978
I'm okay with it,

51:47.562 --> 51:49.314
but she must've been very surprised.

51:50.732 --> 51:51.858
Just for a moment.

51:52.609 --> 51:55.654
She's very open-minded,
so she understands.

51:56.363 --> 51:57.739
She probably hates me now.

51:59.032 --> 52:00.450
No, she's really not like that.

52:03.703 --> 52:04.788
I told my mom

52:05.997 --> 52:07.707
that there's someone I like.

52:09.960 --> 52:11.253
And what did she say?

52:15.423 --> 52:16.383
What is it?

52:17.092 --> 52:18.385
You can't tell me?

52:20.595 --> 52:21.638
She cried.

52:24.182 --> 52:25.725
She must've been very surprised.

52:30.230 --> 52:31.231
Ji-ho.

52:32.065 --> 52:33.775
It must've been very hard for you.

52:40.282 --> 52:43.702
I told you that I'll go to you
without hurting you.

52:44.327 --> 52:46.079
I'll make sure you won't have to sigh.

52:47.873 --> 52:50.333
But I want to make sure
you won't have a hard time.

52:52.002 --> 52:54.004
If you don't cause any trouble,
I'll be fine.

52:55.422 --> 52:56.464
I'll be good to you.

52:57.883 --> 52:58.925
It goes both ways.

52:59.342 --> 53:02.137
We'll be good to each other.

53:03.555 --> 53:04.681
This feels surreal.

53:05.974 --> 53:07.058
What?

53:08.727 --> 53:10.020
You and I...

53:12.272 --> 53:13.440
are "we" now.

53:18.361 --> 53:19.362
Come in.

53:22.282 --> 53:24.534
We'll have lunch as well,

53:25.327 --> 53:27.412
so pick somewhere quiet.

53:28.830 --> 53:31.041
Yes, don't pick a place
that is hard to get to.

53:31.458 --> 53:32.584
Okay, all right.

53:34.711 --> 53:37.255
These are suggestions
from the Parents' Association.

53:39.966 --> 53:42.469
By the way, your daughter is quite daring.

53:43.887 --> 53:45.722
She called and asked me to meet up.

53:47.015 --> 53:49.643
- Jeong-in called you?
- You didn't know?

53:50.060 --> 53:51.686
No, I didn't. My apologies.

53:52.145 --> 53:53.772
Why are you apologizing?

53:53.855 --> 53:56.149
I mean, if it was about meeting you...

53:56.608 --> 53:58.652
why didn't she say anything to me?

53:58.735 --> 54:00.278
She wants to meet me alone.

54:02.364 --> 54:05.951
Are you saying she requested
a one-on-one meeting with you?

54:06.034 --> 54:07.369
Yes, she did.

54:10.038 --> 54:11.164
I'm excited to meet her.

56:04.319 --> 56:06.363
- We'll order in a few minutes.
- Sure.

56:07.906 --> 56:10.408
Nice to meet you. I'm Lee Jeong-in.

56:10.950 --> 56:12.035
Nice to meet you.

56:13.620 --> 56:14.662
Let's sit down.

56:22.587 --> 56:23.755
- Have a seat.
- Okay.

56:26.800 --> 56:28.510
Shall we eat first?

56:29.386 --> 56:30.762
Whatever you prefer.

56:31.554 --> 56:34.307
We're not really here to eat,
so let's talk first.

56:35.058 --> 56:38.061
I'm sure you wanted to meet me alone
for a reason.

56:40.480 --> 56:44.567
I thought it'd be best to come alone
as I'll predominantly be talking about

56:44.651 --> 56:46.236
my personal thoughts and opinions.

56:47.445 --> 56:49.656
I heard you've known Gi-seok
for quite a while.

56:51.366 --> 56:54.786
We've been in a relationship
for four years.

56:59.666 --> 57:03.586
I know that you don't approve of me.

57:05.130 --> 57:07.882
Yes, I admit that it hurt my self-esteem,

57:08.925 --> 57:10.093
and it upset me as well.

57:10.927 --> 57:14.931
But it's not like we started dating
with marriage in mind,

57:15.640 --> 57:19.436
so I never really showed it.

57:25.066 --> 57:26.860
I'll put all this away when I'm done.

57:30.822 --> 57:33.116
So, you want to read dinosaur books.
Anything else?

57:35.618 --> 57:36.828
I want to see the teacher.

57:38.830 --> 57:40.707
I told you she's not here today.

57:41.583 --> 57:43.001
Then why are we here?

57:44.252 --> 57:45.795
To read books.

57:46.796 --> 57:47.922
Water. I want water.

57:49.090 --> 57:50.175
Okay, just a second.

57:57.807 --> 57:58.933
Oh, hello.

58:01.186 --> 58:02.812
Jeong-in is off today.

58:03.897 --> 58:05.315
I'm not here to see her.

58:08.985 --> 58:10.487
You're here with your nephew.

58:11.738 --> 58:14.699
Still, you should've come on a day
when Jeong-in is here.

58:17.452 --> 58:19.037
- Enjoy your lunch.
- You too.

58:38.264 --> 58:40.892
I've heard some things about you,

58:42.143 --> 58:44.979
but you actually seem
a lot more upright and straightforward.

58:45.063 --> 58:46.898
I apologize if I came across as rude.

58:46.981 --> 58:48.274
No, not at all.

58:49.275 --> 58:51.319
Being opinionated is a good thing.

58:51.903 --> 58:54.906
I got a sense that even your father
is somewhat intimidated by you.

58:55.490 --> 58:57.033
It's a compliment.

58:59.077 --> 59:02.121
Thank you
for thinking highly of my father.

59:03.623 --> 59:04.999
What are you trying to say?

59:05.750 --> 59:08.002
I heard that you gave him a great offer.

59:09.504 --> 59:12.882
You've been successfully leading
the foundation for years,

59:13.466 --> 59:16.469
so the fact that you chose
to hire my father after his retirement

59:17.095 --> 59:19.764
shows that you deeply trust him, right?

59:22.850 --> 59:25.103
Regardless of Gi-seok's relationship
with me,

59:25.562 --> 59:27.272
you still made such a decision.

59:28.314 --> 59:29.774
I'm incredibly grateful,

59:30.817 --> 59:34.529
and it taught me the importance of keeping
personal feelings separate from work.

59:35.697 --> 59:36.990
Has Jeong-in called at all?

59:38.825 --> 59:40.368
Take this and go somewhere else.

59:41.494 --> 59:45.039
You keep asking me every five minutes.
Why are you so antsy?

59:45.331 --> 59:47.292
You're her mom. Aren't you worried at all?

59:47.542 --> 59:49.127
Why should I be worried?

59:49.210 --> 59:51.087
It's not like she did something wrong.

59:51.629 --> 59:55.133
She has a short fuse, you know.
I'm worried she might be rude to him.

59:55.216 --> 59:56.509
I mean, she'll speak out.

59:57.093 --> 59:59.554
But she won't be rude or discourteous.

01:00:01.097 --> 01:00:02.807
If anything, you'll ruin it all.

01:00:04.017 --> 01:00:05.643
If she calls, tell me right away.

01:01:29.143 --> 01:01:32.021
UNEXPECTEDLY YOU

01:01:46.536 --> 01:01:49.330
It seems like Gi-seok wants to marry you.

01:01:51.124 --> 01:01:52.875
Have you two talked about it?

01:01:57.922 --> 01:01:59.257
Yes, we have talked about it.

01:02:01.259 --> 01:02:03.553
It doesn't sound like
you two are on the same page.

01:02:05.763 --> 01:02:07.014
I'm sorry.

01:02:09.058 --> 01:02:10.226
For what?

01:02:13.062 --> 01:02:14.105
I...

01:02:15.273 --> 01:02:16.816
don't want to get married.

01:02:53.853 --> 01:02:56.481
We need to stop him.
He's no match for Gi-seok.

01:02:56.564 --> 01:02:57.482
Who can stop him?

01:02:57.565 --> 01:02:59.984
Have you seen him giving up
when he set his mind?

01:03:00.067 --> 01:03:01.068
Eun-u isn't me.

01:03:01.152 --> 01:03:03.196
I can put up with anything, but not Eun-u.

01:03:03.279 --> 01:03:05.990
I won't forgive anyone who hurts my son.

01:03:06.532 --> 01:03:07.742
I'm sorry, Gi-seok.

01:03:07.825 --> 01:03:10.286
Someone's stealing his girlfriend.
Can't think rationally.

01:03:10.369 --> 01:03:11.954
I bet he's lost it.

01:03:12.038 --> 01:03:14.373
Gi-seok is there?
Probably there to see Ji-ho.

01:03:14.457 --> 01:03:17.502
I want to be honest and tell everything.

01:03:17.585 --> 01:03:18.753
Can I do that?

01:03:18.836 --> 01:03:20.880
Will you keep joking?
Do you think I'm stupid?

01:03:20.963 --> 01:03:22.965
I'm telling you the truth.
Why are you angry?

01:03:23.049 --> 01:03:25.510
I've decided to stop wondering

01:03:25.968 --> 01:03:28.429
whether or not
I deserve to ask you to be with me.

01:03:28.888 --> 01:03:30.306
I'm just going to love you.

01:03:30.890 --> 01:03:34.852
I realized Yu Ji-ho loves Lee Jeong-in.

01:03:38.564 --> 01:03:40.566
Subtitle translation by Liya Choi
